title: Watch: White House holds briefing as Trump gets set to leave for Switzerland
text:
Watch: White House holds briefing as Trump gets set to leave for Switzerland 11 Mins Ago CNBC.com If you are experiencing issues watching this video, tap here to view it in your browser. SHARES 
[ The stream is slated to start at 3:30 p.m., ET. Please refresh the page if you do not see a player above at that time. ] 
The White House briefs reporters on Tuesday ahead of President Donald Trump 's planned trip to the World Economic Forum in Switzerland. 
White House officials will likely also face questions about Attorney General Jeff Sessions' interview with Russia investigation special counsel Robert Mueller's team. CNBC NEWSLETTERS
